headline: Jack Henry Recognized in U.S. News & World Report's 2025 - 2026 Best Companies to Work For
summary: Jack Henry™ (Nasdaq: JKHY) has been named one of the 2025 – 2026 Best Companies to Work For by U.S. News & World Report. This marks the second consecutive year Jack Henry has earned this prestigious recognition, highlighting the company's commitment to supporting its employees and fostering a positive experience throughout their careers.
